- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a new approach for regression problems using soft regression models and optimization of loss functions, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The proposed approach involves instance-dependent optimization, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper mentions the use of the proposed approach for image segmentation, which is a common problem in computer vision. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the conversion of one-parameter crisp regression models into two-parameter soft regression models, which involves the use of data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.ST (Statistics): The paper deals with regression models and loss functions, which are fundamental concepts in statistics.
